<para style="p">

  <verse number="12" style="v" />When I send Artemas or Tychicus to you, do your best to come to me at the town of Nicopolis, because I have decided to spend the winter there.

  <verse number="13" style="v" />Do everything you can to send Zenas, the law expert, and Apollos on their journey, along with everything that they need.
